SetInCountry: Canada
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Trina Stewart
AuthorCountry: Canada
Text: "I am recently separated.  I have suffered trauma due to my husband\u2019s surprise\
  \ drug addiction and infidelity.  After trying to save the marriage, I am now on\
  \ my own after 32 years.  I am trying to find my purpose by exploring new terrorities\
  \ and cultures.  I am ready to experience new things to create a new beginning at\
  \ 46 years old."
